.row
  .col-sm-6
    %p Swarmize is a data journalism platform.  It helps editors collect, analyze and output information using basic web forms, helpful charts and developer-friendly APIs.

    %p Whether asking questions through a survey or engaging users through complex interactives Swarmize aims to handle the difficult aspects of managing large amounts of fast-moving data. 

    %p Data journalism shouldn't be a software problem.

    %p Want your users to tell you about the weather? Interested in tracking behavior of a Twitter hashtag? Need a way to poll people while they are watching politicians debate on TV? 

    %p Read the case studies below for information about how Swarmize can help make data journalism easier and more compelling. 

